title: Dual frequency shrink tunnel machine US-BSS-5030X
title_uz: Qadoqni qizdirish orqali qisqartirish uchun ikki chastotali uskuna (termo qadoqlash)  US-BSS-5030X
title_en: Dual frequency shrink tunnel machine US-BSS-5030X
short_description: This US-BSS-5030X equipment shrinks pre-packaged product packaging by heating it to fit the product size. The equipment works at a voltage of 380V, the frequency speed is 50-60Hz, the power is 21kW, and the size of the equipment is 1800*1060*1150 mm. The weight is 385 kg.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-BSS-5030X uskuna tayyor qadoqlangan mahsulot qadog'ini qizdirish orqali qisqartiradi va mahsulot hajmiga moslashtiradi. Uskuna 380V kuchlanishda ishlaydi, chastota tezligi 50-60Hz, quvvati 21kW va uskuna hajmi 1800*1060*1150 mm ni tashkil qiladi. Vazni esa 385 kg.
short_description_ru: Это оборудование US-BSS-5030X сжимает упаковку предварительно упакованного продукта, нагревая ее до размера продукта. Оборудование работает при напряжении 380В, частота вращения 50-60Гц, мощность 21кВт, размеры оборудования 1800*1060*1150 мм. Вес 385 кг.
short_description_en: This US-BSS-5030X equipment shrinks pre-packaged product packaging by heating it to fit the product size. The equipment works at a voltage of 380V, the frequency speed is 50-60Hz, the power is 21kW, and the size of the equipment is 1800*1060*1150 mm. The weight is 385 kg.
long_description:
This US-BSS-5030X equipment shrinks pre-packaged product packaging by heating it to fit the product size. The equipment works at a voltage of 380V, the frequency speed is 50-60Hz, the power is 21kW, and the size of the equipment is 1800*1060*1150 mm. The weight is 385 kg.

 

Basic parameters
Model US-BSS-5030X
Voltage 380V, 50-60Hz
Power 21kW
Dimension 1800*1060*1150 mm
Tunnel size 1500*500*300 mm
Conveying speed 0-15 m/min
Transport load 50 kg
Applicable film PVC, POF
Weight 385 kg

Ushbu US-BSS-5030X uskuna tayyor qadoqlangan mahsulot qadog'ini qizdirish orqali qisqartiradi va mahsulot hajmiga moslashtiradi. Uskuna 380V kuchlanishda ishlaydi, chastota tezligi 50-60Hz, quvvati 21kW va uskuna hajmi 1800*1060*1150 mm ni tashkil qiladi. Vazni esa 385 kg.
